title: Program Your Mind For Victory | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Program Your Mind For Victory | Joel Osteen
description:
If you want to draw in the good things of God, you have to program your mind for victory. Choose to dwell on the promise instead of the doubt. You have everything you need to fulfill your purpose.


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
